data.description: This beautiful home is located in the award winning Dorchester II School District and is just minutes from the airport, Boeing, Mercedes and Bosch. The home features many upgrades: crown molding in formal dining; engineered hardwoods in family room, office area,  formal dining, & formal living room; a fireplace; ceiling fans in all bedrooms; Energy Savings Features-Solar Panels and Solar attic Fan. The frog is a bedroom/ bonus room; screened porch; plus a garden tub and shower in owners suite bathroom. The home also features gutters, and a irrigation system.  There is a downstairs bedroom and a full bathroom, perfect for guests.  The laundry room is conveniently located upstairs.As you enter the home, the two story foyer leads to the dining room to the left or to a home office to the right. The family room has a beautiful fireplace and lots of windows to let the natural light into the room. The kitchen features stainless appliances and eat in kitchen. A French door leads to the beautiful screened porch. The screened porch features tile flooring and leads out into the beautifully landscaped back yard. Complete with a water feature and two garden beds.  A great place to entertain and relax...A great place to call home.
